      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 397,
      "message": "getYangResourceEntities executes a query for each ModuleReference. Consider replacing it with a bulk query to reduce database calls.\n\nSomthing like below:\n\nprivate Set<YangResourceEntity> getYangResourceEntities(final Collection<ModuleReference> moduleReferences) {\n    Set<String> moduleNames = moduleReferences.stream()\n            .map(ModuleReference::getModuleName)\n            .collect(Collectors.toSet());\n\n    return yangResourceRepository.findAllByModuleNames(moduleNames);\n}\n\nThis reduces database queries from N calls to a single batch query.",
